data.value:
This is a free software used for converting the relation between NRI(SGSN), GUMMEI(MME) and GUAMI(AMF) in a pool solution.
Based on the relation of the IDs, the UE can be mounted to an unique node during inter-system-changing between 2/3/4/5G.
Version 1 (2019-11-08) - The basic function of IDs converting between NRI, GUMMEI and GUAMI.
